				<wikidot:authorName>weizhong</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1777811</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's not bad. The dialogue is solid, and the writing is fine. My issue mostly stems from the fact that the effect is played a bit too straight for me and becomes a fairly obvious plot from the start, and the rest of the story doesn't really build anything new, nor was it compelling enough for me to overlook the simple plot.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
